@startuml
title DoconnectAI - System Sequence Diagram

actor User

participant UserController
participant QuestionController
participant AnswerController
participant CommentController
participant VoteController
participant ChatMessageController
participant AiController

participant UserServiceImpl
participant QuestionServiceImpl
participant AnswerServiceImpl
participant CommentServiceImpl
participant VoterServiceImpl
participant ChatMessageServiceImpl
participant AIClientService

database Database

== Registration/Login ==
User -> UserController : Register/Login
UserController -> UserServiceImpl : authenticate()
UserServiceImpl -> Database : User Data

== Ask Question ==
User -> QuestionController : Ask Question
QuestionController -> QuestionServiceImpl : saveQuestion()
QuestionServiceImpl -> Database : Store Question

== Post Answer ==
User -> AnswerController : Post Answer
AnswerController -> AnswerServiceImpl : saveAnswer()
AnswerServiceImpl -> Database : Store Answer

== Comment ==
User -> CommentController : Add Comment
CommentController -> CommentServiceImpl : saveComment()
CommentServiceImpl -> Database : Store Comment

== Vote ==
User -> VoteController : Upvote/Downvote
VoteController -> VoterServiceImpl : vote()
VoterServiceImpl -> Database : Update Vote

== Chat ==
User -> ChatMessageController : Send Message
ChatMessageController -> ChatMessageServiceImpl : saveMessage()
ChatMessageServiceImpl -> Database : Store Message

== AI Query ==
User -> AiController : Ask AI
AiController -> AIClientService : generateResponse()
AIClientService -> Database : Store History (optional)

@enduml